metadata.name: Who am I?
metadata.description:
My imagination goes crazy and at times I fall tangent to my own thoughts. Going down a road of uncertainty now realizing what's certain of me, finally catching the same mistake and dreaming of different hopes you see. I wont let these fuzzy thoughts take control of me.

Fuzzy and who he is in his essence. 
When you listen, or read ask yourself: "Who am I?"
